OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FStaying hot, sunny and mostly dry over
OL,7,Fthe next few days across Wales with
OL,8,Fthe odd isolated thunderstorm. A
OL,9,Flittle more patchy cloud on Thursday,
OL,10,Fperhaps with a shower.
